# aeda OS — Project Instructions

Last updated: July 2026 — Slices 1–6 live

## What Is This

aeda OS is the internal operating system for aeda (VanCoin LLC), a non-custodial EURC wallet company. It consists of:

1. **aeda-workspace** — Next.js frontend deployed on Vercel
2. **aeda-os-worker** — Node.js background worker deployed on Railway

The system provides an AI-powered workspace where agents (Claude-powered personas) handle tasks, review documents, process intelligence, and coordinate work.

---

## Features Built

### Slice 1–3 — Core Workspace
- Agent chat system with streaming responses
- Task board (Kanban) with assignments, priorities, due dates
- Room-based collaboration (Marketing, Legal, Product, Board Room, Fundraising, Training)
- Org chart visualization
- Project management with active project tracking

### Slice 4 — OS Dashboard at /os-dashboard
- Daily cost tracking per agent/job
- Audit log of all LLM calls
- Cost rollup job (system.costRollup) runs 03:30 Prague daily

### Slice 5A — Knowledge Feed at /knowledge
- Three-tier knowledge injection via getKnowledgeFeed():
  - Tier 1: Permanent organization knowledge (targetAgents filter)
  - Tier 2: Temporary intelligence items (14-day TTL)
  - Tier 3: Professional knowledge targeted at specific agents
  - Tier 4: Approved vault standards by agent role (Brand/Copy/Compliance/Design Standards — only when standardApproved: true)
- Trust levels: fact (✓), analysis (△), signal (○)
- Source types: official, media, research, company
- Quality gates: signalScore ≤ 3 blocked, linkedin_general/social/inferred blocked

### Slice 5B — Fundraising Intel at /fundraising-intel
- Weekly funding rounds display
- Funding opportunities pipeline
- @hasmik agentic intelligence gathering
- Investor → opportunity matching

### Slice 6 — Document Vault at /vault
- Three-tab UI: Documents / Templates / Standards
- Upload PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX with custom categories
- Claude-native PDF text extraction (claude-sonnet-4-6)
- MongoDB storage — R2 binary storage enabled (write token fixed July 2026)
- Standards approval flow — Approve & Activate button
- Tier 4 agent injection: approved standards inject into relevant agents via getKnowledgeFeed() (Brand Standard → tatev/mike/ruzan/sofi, Compliance Standard → narek/all external-facing agents, Design Standard → mike, Copy Standard → ruzan/sofi/tatev)
- Manual status selector per document (Pending/Reviewed/Flagged)
- Soft archive (no hard delete)
- permanentDoc flag blocks archive on corporate/regulatory documents
- Sidebar restructured: Intelligence / Fundraising / Work / Rooms / Company / Agents

