## Architecture Notes

### Agent Context Injection

Every agent chat message is enriched with:
1. Agent system prompt (from `src/lib/agents.ts`)
2. Knowledge feed (getKnowledgeFeed with 4 tiers)
3. Task context (if mentioned)
4. Investor context (if @arshak and investor mentioned)

### Vault Standards Flow

1. Upload standard document (Brand/Copy/Compliance/Design)
2. Claude extracts text content (claude-sonnet-4-6)
3. Document saved with extractionStatus: completed
4. User clicks "Approve & Activate"
5. standardApproved: true, standardApprovedBy: "artur"
6. getKnowledgeFeed() injects into relevant agents via STANDARD_ROUTING

### Hasmik Intelligence Loop

1. Triggered Monday 19:00 Prague (or manual via /api/os/trigger-hasmik)
2. agentLoop runs with claude-sonnet-4-6
3. Tools available: web_search, write_knowledge_entry, write_fundraising_round, write_funding_opportunity, write_inbox_signal
4. Quality gates enforce: signalScore > 3, valid sourceType, sourceUrl required for score > 5
5. Haiku verification pass reviews all entries, removes low-quality
6. Results saved to MongoDB (KnowledgeEntry, FundraisingRound, FundingOpportunity)

